statements: SELECT * FROM FoodCompliance;
SELECT supplier_name, location, sustainability_rating FROM FoodCompliance;

SELECT supplier_name, location FROM FoodCompliance WHERE sustainability_rating > 4.0;
SELECT supplier_id, supplier_name, location, sustainability_rating FROM FoodCompliance ORDER BY supplier_name DESC;

SELECT * FROM FoodCompliance ORDER BY location ASC, supplier_name DESC;

SELECT AVG(sustainability_rating) AS avg_rating, COUNT(*) AS total_suppliers FROM FoodCompliance;

SELECT product_name, price, supplier_name, distributor_name FROM product JOIN supplier ON product.supplier_id = supplier.supplier_id JOIN distributor ON product.distributor_id = distributor.distributor_id WHERE price < 1000 ORDER BY price DESC;

SELECT distributor_name, compliance_status, COUNT(*) AS total_products FROM distributor JOIN product ON distributor.distributor_id = product.distributor_id GROUP BY distributor_name, compliance_status HAVING total_products > 5;

SELECT supplier_name, supplier_location, SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM supplier JOIN product ON supplier.supplier_id = product.supplier_id GROUP BY supplier_name, supplier_location ORDER BY total_quantity DESC;

SELECT supplier_name, supplier_location, compliance_date FROM supplier JOIN sustainability_data ON supplier.supplier_id = sustainability_data.supplier_id WHERE compliance_date >= '2022-01-01' AND compliance_date <= '2022-06-30' ORDER BY compliance_date ASC;
